The boiler fire is first brought to the highest level and the water boils, then the boiler fire is brought to a lower level and a constant heat is obtained.
Vegetables and nutrients cooked in the steam for about 10-15 minutes are checked with the help of forks after thoroughly cooking.
Vegetables that are cooked are taken from the stove and placed in plates and served.
In the technique of steam cooking, the appearance, color and smell of the food do not change, so this method is healthy.
The taste of the food remains the same.
